Package edu.ncsu.csc216.garage.model.service_garage

Class Garage

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.garage.model.service_garage.Garage
  • public class Garage
extends java.lang.Object
    Concrete class representing a garage that consists of a collection of service bays. A newly instantiated Garage will initialize the number of open bays to 8 by default. The Garage class will handle the management of the arrays of service bays it represents by adding bays, releasing cars from bays, and managing the array's size.
    Author:
    Will Parker, Christine Park
